<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT31">
<l>mēṉāṉ mukaṉaraṉai yiṭṭaviṭu cāpan</l>
<l>tāṉṉā raṇaṉoḻittāṉ tārakaiyuḷ vāṉōr</l>
<l>perumāṉai yēttāta pēykāḷ piṟakkuṅ</l>
<l>karumāyam pēciṟ katai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Formerly, it was Nārāyaṇa who destroyed the curse</l>
<l>placed by the four-faced [Brahmā] on Hara-Śiva on this earth.</l>
<l>O demons who do not extol the Lord of celestials!</l>
<l>If one speaks of the wonder of the foetus that is born,</l>
<l rend="indent">[it would be] a [long] story.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
